From 216feb94a4dae4db08fa078f5d732853543f5361 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Joshua (local)" <dev@findmynyumba.local>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2026 12:41:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(media): extend multi-photo/video support to landlord
 flow (Option B)

Brings landlords to parity with student-host using the SAME ListingMedia infra:
- landlords.py: media helpers; create/update gain media field alongside images
  (backward compatible); get_properties + get_property return media + cover_url.
- dashboard-landlord.html: branded uploader replaces single photo input; submit
  sends media with progress; cards use gallery carousel (cover, arrows, swipe,
  video badge, lightbox).
- contact-landlord.html: thumbnail prefers cover_url, falls back to image_url.

Verified on SQLite: full landlord chain, mixed photo/video, legacy fallback.
